Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.65,0:01:26.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}独个儿寂寞难耐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:33.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}于是牵住了伙伴的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:39.02,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}这样的话将永远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.27,0:01:43.98,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}活在童年无忧的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:51.65,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}无论如何都想要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:57.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}伙伴们曾牵在一起的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:02:04.46,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}已变得七零八落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:08.38,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}一个个渐渐离去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:15.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}向着那苏醒之日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:24.52,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}迈开脚步毅然前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:33.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}仿佛节日的喧嚣过后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:39.12,OPCN,NTP,0,0,1,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}只留下了寂寞
