Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:40.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}那天你牵起我的手说道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.76,0:19:49.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}向往着那墙外面的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:55.73,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}轻轻抱着我柔弱的肩头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:20:03.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}穿梭于黑暗的各个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:10.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}两人向往的梦遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:19.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}两人放弃的梦遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:32.92,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}两人开始了夏日的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:40.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}一步步走来充满痛与苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:48.16,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你为我而买来的那烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:55.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}没有能消除内心的忧郁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:21:03.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}两人向往的梦遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:11.96,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}两人放弃的梦遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:20.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}琐碎的日常也倾注了爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:27.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}又增添了许多流浪的猫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.67,0:21:39.82,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}身旁的你总是笑容满面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:49.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}散步回来再次听见钟声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:57.53,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}引得泪水不禁悄然滑落
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:04.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}挣开我的手你飞奔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:12.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}黑夜依然在拒绝你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:20.13,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}两人向往的梦遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:28.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}两人放弃的梦遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:37.01,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}冰冷的雨淋着孤单的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.01,0:22:44.51,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}忽然看见眼前的绊脚石
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:52.15,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}我抱起浑身是伤的猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.15,0:22:59.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}你我将会被一直守护着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:11.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}能把这意义忘了有多好
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------TEXT--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.45,0:00:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切全是恭介策划的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从最开始的那天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介他回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以棒球为借口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.44,0:00:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让铃去交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在信中留下课题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以此让铃成长起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:02.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是计划好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.39,0:01:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.11,0:01:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让铃能独当一面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛露出这种表情  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是要去拯救受到创伤的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去兄弟校了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  打起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.07,0:03:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一直让我憧憬着的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.02,0:03:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经越走越远了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从小就一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如今…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道大家是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家似乎在朝着各自的方向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于这件事我即便有想法也不会说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直以来都这么决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人早就知道恭介的计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夹在我们中间  给他造成痛苦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说你认为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:46.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切是恭介为了铃能独立而写好的剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介是想让怕生的铃经历点东西来成长的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这出发点并没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:05:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这次的做法我实在看不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法原谅的是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介早就做好了解散的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.13,0:05:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才建立的棒球队Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大家一起打棒球的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是最棒的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想如此快乐的时光要是能一直持续下去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还相信恭介也怀着同样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是恭介从一开始就是打算把铃送走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:29.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让Little Busters就此结束的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:39.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树  你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友情的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,印证
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不找别人商量  随随便便让它结束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是很过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:05:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:06:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为就算铃不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters也不会就这样完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使其他人全都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人也会让它继续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.39,0:06:24.22,up,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}道具之中也寄宿着灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟谦吾想的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.42,0:06:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远坚持着Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树  我不知道该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身边全是不认识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都阴沉着脸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人可以说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人找我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直孤零零的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:07.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油啊  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:14.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「加油」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么不负责任的一个词
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己不用背负任何责任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20}老师跟我说\N为什么会选我来\N谁知道啊  呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我只能这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃根本不可能去鼓励他人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还只是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树  小毬的手机也接不通了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃好像给小毬同学发了很多条短信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但全都发不出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.79,0:07:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这边也接不通小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被拉到黑名单了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是恭介  对铃的手机动了手脚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此没有其他可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然连小毬同学也要隔开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么想都觉得太过分
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来谷同学和库特她们请假  也是恭介指使的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他女生已经没有利用价值了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有必要做到这一步吗  无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感到了隔阂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经加不起油了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃真的在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.26,0:09:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.33,0:09:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去接铃回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃…她在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤零零留在陌生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连恭介你也没见过铃哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.68,0:09:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是因为我一直在保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次也保护一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.19,0:09:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么粗暴的手段  根本不会有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会失去更为宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们培育至今的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许许多多宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介你想把它们付诸一炬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周末我会设法让她回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.87,0:10:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  在这周末之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管有多难受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我熬过去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周末回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事能由恭介说了算吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说  恭介会设法达成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃  想喝点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.70,0:11:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我叫小毬同学过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给她看见这个样子  会让她担心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想错了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以为铃离开我们能得到成长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才把她送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是铃现在身心疲惫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:52.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虚弱得无法说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但明天恭介一定会让她回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:11:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.50,0:12:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续下去的话铃会崩溃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾  我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路只有一条
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和恭介战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去和恭介战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能赢得了恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一点都不强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是只有你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:13:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是剑拔弩张  两人一起上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决一胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赢了  就不让铃回兄弟校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.95,0:13:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远和我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赢了的话铃就要回那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用什么分胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悉听尊便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还是用棒球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让队友来扔球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能首先将球打出场外三回的队伍胜出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那你要跟谁组队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.55,0:13:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于到你的肌肉派上用场的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别烦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是为了这种事才锻炼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:46.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来决定先攻后攻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面还是反面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是正面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪边比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不练习直接上场的话  后攻好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人  尽全力挥棒就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会扔出让你全垒打的好球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有那么容易
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我可不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人的自尊不会允许他输给谦吾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以真人会不管游戏目的  全力奋战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这大概也在恭介的计算之内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么的讽刺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儿时的四个好朋友  如今却针锋相对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:14:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.65,0:15:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能先将球打出场外三回的队伍胜出吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会先绕臂再投球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先由第一球来抓住时机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无效球只能有这一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞行距离足够了  下次能行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.76,0:15:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谦吾你击球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我能扔中好球区
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾就一定能打中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是谦吾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论身体素质还是心理素质都比其他人要强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我好好投球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能赢下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都别想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么投出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  下次就能打中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子是拖不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,场外球只打一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一球定胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.24,0:16:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:37.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来  拿出本事了  真人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们瞧瞧你的肌肉是不是浪得虚名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧不瞧都不是浪得虚名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都在全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还真是可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:17:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一球  我们打不中就输了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么好害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树  相信你的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫泽谦吾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.82,0:17:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最强的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.89,0:17:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来了  谦吾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然玩这种把戏！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.31,0:18:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负已定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:18.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters已经不是我的归宿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃离这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两人一起离开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（致真人）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:06.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是要跟小毬说一声
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想让她担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可不能把小毬同学再牵扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.97,0:20:25.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能放开这只手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要靠自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护铃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.52,0:21:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去跟大家一起玩的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心底已经察觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.11,0:22:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弱小的我  无法保护铃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.98,0:23:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长久以来  我忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.52,0:23:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要活着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会有所失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界里有你所不知道的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.63,0:23:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  5月13日
